<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُحَمَّدٌ:</span> <span class="c2">(قَادِرِينَ)</span> حَالٌ بِمَعْنَى: بَلَى نَجْمَعُهَا قَادِرِينَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>